{"tha-ap298:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap298:0.2":"Citakapujakavagga ","tha-ap298:0.3":"6 Padapujakattheraapadana ","tha-ap298:1.1":"“Pabbate himavantamhi, ","tha-ap298:1.2":"ahosim kinnaro tada; ","tha-ap298:1.3":"Addasam virajam buddham, ","tha-ap298:1.4":"pitaramsimva bhanumam. ","tha-ap298:2.1":"Upetam tamaham buddham, ","tha-ap298:2.2":"vipassim lokanayakam; ","tha-ap298:2.3":"Candanam tagarancapi, ","tha-ap298:2.4":"pade osincaham tada. ","tha-ap298:3.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap298:3.2":"yam padam abhipujayim; ","tha-ap298:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap298:3.4":"padapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap298:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap298:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap298:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap298:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma padapujako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap298:6.1":"Padapujakattherassapadanam chattham. "}